Name:                streamgraph
Version:             0.0.0

Description:
  
  Library for creating stream graphs.  The supported output format is
  currently svg.  See this research for more information:
  http://www.leebyron.com/else/streamgraph/

License:             BSD3
Author:              Jason Dagit
Maintainer:          dagitj@gmail.com
Build-Type:          Simple
Cabal-Version:       >=1.8
Category:            Graphics

library
  Hs-Source-Dirs:    src
  Exposed-Modules:   Graphics.StreamGraph
  Build-Depends:     base >= 3 && < 5,
                     wumpus-core == 0.13.*
  ghc-options:       -Wall -fno-warn-unused-binds

Executable examples
  Hs-Source-Dirs:    src
  Main-is:           Examples.hs
  Build-depends:     base >= 3 && < 5,
                     wumpus-core == 0.13.*
  ghc-options:       -Wall -fno-warn-unused-binds
  Other-modules:     Graphics.StreamGraph
